Class RegexBuilderMainPresenter

    BindHandler, com.google.gwt.event.shared.EventHandler

    public class RegexBuilderMainPresenter
extends BatchClassInlinePresenter<RegexBuilderMainView>
    Provides the functionality to handle events for RegexBuilderMainView. This presenter also handles the events for Regex Tester utility.
    Version:
    1.0 $LastChangedDate:$
    $LastChangedRevision:$
